### Manual API Tests for Week Creation System
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code, or import into Postman

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@partnershipId = YOUR_PARTNERSHIP_ID_HERE

### Test 1: Get Week Settings
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/partnerships/{{partnershipId}}/week-settings

### Test 2: Disable Auto-Creation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/partnerships/{{partnershipId}}/week-settings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "autocreateweeks": false
}

### Test 3: Re-enable Auto-Creation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/partnerships/{{partnershipId}}/week-settings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "autocreateweeks": true
}

### Test 4: Pause Until Specific Date
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/partnerships/{{partnershipId}}/week-settings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weekcreationpauseduntil": "2025-12-31T23:59:59Z"
}

### Test 5: Clear Pause
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/partnerships/{{partnershipId}}/week-settings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weekcreationpauseduntil": null
}

### Test 6: Get Settings Again (Verify)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/partnerships/{{partnershipId}}/week-settings

